[[Exar Kun/Legends|Exar Kun]] was known to wear various types of [[Armor/Legends|armored]] suits, including a customized '''light battle suit''' which offered considerable protection despite its weight and maintained good flexibility.

Soon after the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]] was [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|destroyed]], a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] treasure hunter named [[Suz Tanwa]] found what she reported to be Exar Kun's light battle suit on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]], which her ancestor, [[Suvam Tan]] had hidden in a storage pod. The suit that she found had a [[cortosis-weave]] construction.<ref name="TBRO">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040722yavin|text=Yavin: The Big Red One|int=Yavin: The Big Red One}}</ref>

